column2: SELECT TOP #   a.OBJID AS OBJID,   a.RA AS RA,   a.DEC AS DEC,      sp.z AS zsp,   sp.zErr AS e_zsp,   sp.class AS class,   sp.subClass AS subClass,   sp.zWarning AS zWarning,   sp.mode AS mode,      sp.psfMag_u AS umag,   sp.psfMag_g AS gmag,   sp.psfMag_r AS rmag,   sp.psfMag_i AS imag,   sp.psfMag_z AS zmag,   sp.psfMagErr_u AS e_umag,   sp.psfMagErr_g AS e_gmag,   sp.psfMagErr_r AS e_rmag,   sp.psfMagErr_i AS e_imag,   sp.psfMagErr_z AS e_zmag,    from   MyDB.akari AS a,   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.RA, m.RA, #) AS n   JOIN SpecPhotoAll as sp ON n.objid = sp.objid
